edu.umd.cs.psl.model.atom

Class AtomEvent

  • java.lang.Object
    • edu.umd.cs.psl.model.atom.AtomEvent

  • public class AtomEvent
extends java.lang.Object
    An event related to a RandomVariableAtom.

    An AtomEvent provides two pieces of information in addition to the type of event: the RandomVariableAtom that caused the event and the AtomEventFramework that created the event.
